  <brief_title>Open Label Study to Assess Safety, PK and Explore Efficacy of OPRX-106 in Patients With Active Mild to Moderate Ulcerative Colitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label, Proof of Concept Study to Assess the Safety, PK and Explore Efficacy of OPRX-106 in Patients With Active Mild to Moderate Ulcerative Colitis</official_title>
