  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a proof of concept, randomized, open label, 2-arm study of OPRX-106 in subjects with
      active mild to moderate ulcerative colitis. Eligible subjects will be enrolled and randomized
      to receive 2 mg or 8 mg of OPRX-106 administered orally, once daily for 8 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
